==Spanish==

===Noun===
'''zapallo''' ''m''

# [[zucchini]], [[courgette]]
# [[pumpkin]], [[gourd]]

====Usage notes====
'''Zapallo''' is used predominantly in South America, including Argentina, Chile, Peru and Uraguay, Bolivia, and Panama.  Elsewhere, [[calabaza]] is more commonly used.

